		<title>State of the Word 2024: Watch Live on December 16</title>
		<link>https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/13/state-of-the-word-2024/</link>
					<comments>https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/13/state-of-the-word-2024/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[WordPress.com Staff]]></dc:creator>
