		<link>https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/04/hot-off-the-press-new-wordpress-com-themes-for-december-2024/</link>
					<comments>https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/04/hot-off-the-press-new-wordpress-com-themes-for-december-2024/#comments</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Amanda Coopersmith]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 20:58:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Product Features]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://en.blog.wordpress.com/?p=74926</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Another month, another batch of fresh themes for WordPress.com users.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Another month means another fresh batch of excellent themes for WordPress.com. Let’s look at some of the latest additions to the <a href="https://wordpress.com/themes" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">WordPress.com themes gallery</a>, with great options for content creators, small businesses, event organizers, and personal sites. Preview each one below (and maybe try taking one for a spin).</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/coachava/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">CoachAva</a></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png"><img data-attachment-id="74931" data-permalink="https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/04/hot-off-the-press-new-wordpress-com-themes-for-december-2024/coach-ava-screenshot/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png" data-orig-size="1600,655" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="coach-ava-screenshot" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png?w=1024" width="1024" height="419" src="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-74931" srcset="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png?w=1024 1024w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png?w=150 150w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png?w=300 300w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png?w=768 768w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coach-ava-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Designed for: </strong>Professional coaches</li>



<li><strong>Also great for: </strong>Consultants, thought leaders, speakers, and content creators with paid course offerings</li>
</ul>



<p>With a clean, single-hued design, minimal photography, and approachable fonts, CoachAva is built for professional coaches looking to highlight their core offerings and showcase their expertise.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Whether you’re a seasoned executive coach, a life coach, or a subject matter expert looking to sell digital or in-person services, CoachAva can help you establish trust with potential clients by putting your thought leadership front and center. Blocks make it easy to share blog posts, podcasts, and/or customer testimonials on your homepage. The flexible design makes it easy to define, package, and showcase your different offerings, connecting clients to the perfect programs.</p>



<p><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/coachava/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Explore CoachAva</a></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/castcore/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">CastCore</a></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png"><img data-attachment-id="74932" data-permalink="https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/04/hot-off-the-press-new-wordpress-com-themes-for-december-2024/castcore-screenshot/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png" data-orig-size="1600,590" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="castcore-screenshot" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png?w=1024" width="1024" height="377" src="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-74932" srcset="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png?w=1022 1022w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png?w=150 150w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png?w=300 300w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png?w=768 768w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/castcore-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Best for:</strong> Podcasters</li>



<li><strong>Also great for:</strong> Bloggers, serial content creators, news sites with limited photography</li>
</ul>



<p>Ideal for podcasters building their first site, Castcore features bold, attention-grabbing titles and a minimalist aesthetic that keeps your listeners focused on what matters most – your content.&nbsp;</p>



<p>With a simple homepage design, this template makes it easy for listeners to scroll through your recent content to find the right episode. Castcore is a great option for podcasters who want to build their subscriber base. The <a href="https://wordpress.com/support/wordpress-editor/blocks/podcast-player-block/">Podcast Player block</a> makes it super easy to create an embedded mini-player for your episodes: simply copy your podcast’s RSS URL to engage listeners right on your page. Choose a grey and black color combo for a classic design or go young and bold with bright yellow.</p>



<p><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/castcore/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Explore CastCore</a></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/coachben/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">CoachBen</a></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png"><img data-attachment-id="74933" data-permalink="https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/04/hot-off-the-press-new-wordpress-com-themes-for-december-2024/coachben-screenshot/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png" data-orig-size="1600,722" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="coachben-screenshot" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png?w=1024" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="462" src="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-74933" srcset="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png?w=1024 1024w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png?w=150 150w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png?w=300 300w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png?w=768 768w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/coachben-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Designed for: </strong>Professional coaches</li>



<li><strong>Also great for: </strong>Thought leaders, speakers, and content creators with paid course offerings</li>
</ul>



<p>CoachBen’s dark theme with bright accents offers a bold and professional design that perfectly reflects a coach at the top of their game. Striking and to the point, this theme allows professional coaches to quickly articulate their value proposition and define their services.&nbsp;</p>



<p>With pre-designed blocks for displaying company logos of past clients, a calendar of speaking events, and a blog subscription, there are plenty of ways to show potential clients your expertise and experience. When they’re ready to dig in, they can learn more about specific offerings on your courses page or reach out to schedule a call.</p>



<p><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/coachben/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Explore CoachBen</a></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/greenseed/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">GreenSeed</a></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png"><img data-attachment-id="74935" data-permalink="https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/04/hot-off-the-press-new-wordpress-com-themes-for-december-2024/greenseed-screenshot-2/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png" data-orig-size="1600,729" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="greenseed-screenshot" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png?w=1024" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="466" src="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-74935" srcset="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png?w=1024 1024w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png?w=150 150w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png?w=300 300w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png?w=768 768w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/greenseed-screenshot-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Designed for: </strong>Flexible visual sites</li>



<li><strong>Also Great for:</strong> Brick and mortars, Restaurants, Personal care providers, Digital portfolios, visual artists, photographers</li>
</ul>



<p>Greenseed is a beautifully simple, highly adaptable theme that makes it easy for businesses to take their brick-and-mortar brands online. Designed with full-site editing in mind, Greenseed can be customized to match any brand style, but its open spaces and bold visuals make it a particularly great choice for businesses looking to establish a streamlined online presence that embraces custom photography.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This minimal, approachable layout gives your photos space to breathe while providing key business information like address, phone number, and store hours. Link to your reservations page or provide visitors with a contact form to make it easy for potential customers to make an appointment or plan a visit.</p>



<p><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/greenseed/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Explore Greenseed</a></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/aether/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Aether</a></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png"><img data-attachment-id="74936" data-permalink="https://wordpress.com/blog/2024/12/04/hot-off-the-press-new-wordpress-com-themes-for-december-2024/aether-screenshot/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png" data-orig-size="1600,690" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="aether-screenshot" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png?w=1024" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="441" src="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-74936" srcset="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png?w=1024 1024w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png?w=150 150w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png?w=300 300w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png?w=768 768w, https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2024/11/aether-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Designed for: </strong>Small jewelry or accessory brands</li>



<li><strong>Also great for: </strong>Eco-conscious consumer brands, wedding suppliers&nbsp;</li>
</ul>



<p>Like the jewelry and accessory brands it was built for, Aether embodies modern elegance. With delicate fonts and natural-toned color palettes, this product-focused template offers a tasteful design that allows artisan accessories and jewelry to truly sparkle.&nbsp;</p>



<p>With social media integrations and the ability to highlight products on your homepage, Aether creates a flexible hub for your digital brand. You can allow your customers to purchase products directly through WordPress’s e-commerce plugins or you can link your website to an existing storefront. With Aether, you can be sure your customers will understand your brand&#8217;s commitment to quality and design.</p>



<p><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/aether/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Explore Aether</a></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://wordpress.com/theme/miko/?ref=blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Miko</a></h2>



